## Prior Art Statement

To the best of the author's knowledge, no existing system combines:
- Variable volume expansion chambers as the primary compliance mechanism
- Integrated load sensing through circuit pressure (no external sensors)
- Opposing flow thermal self-regulation
- Threaded servo-to-linear conversion driving sealed hydraulic circuits

in a single unified actuation architecture applicable across scale 
from micro-robotics to heavy industry.

This document establishes the date of conception and sufficient 
technical detail to constitute prior art.

